The '''GP Betonexpressz 2000''' is a [[Europe]]an [[Road bicycle racing|bicycle race]] held in the [[Jász-Nagykun-Szolnok]] County, [[Hungary]]. Since 2009, the race has been organised as a [[1.2]] event on the [[UCI Europe Tour]].

