'''Keskusurheilukenttä''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Kouvola]], [[Finland]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[bandy]] club [[Sudet|Kouvolan Sudet]] (''Wolves''). The stadium holds 12,000.

