{{Infobox football club | clubname = Shorta Aleppo SC | image = | fullname = Shorta Aleppo Sports Club | nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Aleppo 7 April Stadium]], [[Aleppo]] | capacity = 12,500 | chairman = | manager = | league = Syrian League 2nd Division | position = | pattern_la1=|pattern_b1=|pattern_ra1=| leftarm1=|body1=|rightarm1=|shorts1=|socks1=| }}
'''Shorta Aleppo Sports Club''' ({{Lang-ar|'''نادي شرطة حلب الرياضي'''}}) is a [[Syria]]n [[association football|football]] club based in [[Aleppo]]. They play their home games at the [[Aleppo 7 April Stadium]]. Shorta Aleppo played in the [[Syrian Premier League]] twice, in the 1998–1999 and 2000–2001 seasons.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kooora.com/?region=-7&team=6625|title=أرشيف مباريات: شرطة حلب|language=Arabic|access-date=23 October 2017}}</ref>
